# 🤖 Bakome Telegram AI Assistant

A lightweight Telegram bot built for Termux (Android) with memory system and basic security detection.

Created by **Bakome (Fabrice Kitoko Bakome)**.

## 🚀 Features
- Telegram chat bot (real-time messages)
- SQLite memory system (stores user messages)
- Basic scam / suspicious message detection
- Fully compatible with Termux (Android)
- Ready for future AI upgrades

## 📦 Installation
pkg update && pkg upgrade -y  
pkg install python -y  
pkg install git -y  
pip install python-telegram-bot requests  

## ⚙️ Setup
Replace in bot.py:  
TOKEN = "TON_BOT_TOKEN_ICI"

## ▶️ Run
python bot.py

## 🧠 How it works
- Stores messages in SQLite database  
- Detects suspicious keywords like: bitcoin gratuit, urgent, hack, send money  
- Sends warning when detected  

## 🔐 Security Note
This bot is for educational purposes only. It does NOT hack, spy, or access user devices.

